{"about_the_game":"From deep in the Slithering Swamp, Varfa the Ranger and her loyal companion, Orhu, have answered the call to defeat the Uberlich!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">SAY HELLO TO VARFA</h2>Unlock a new playable hero, Varfa the Ranger, featuring more than 50 new items and abilities and unique perks include Scout and Sniper!<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1399020/extras/rosie-header.png?t=1603351686\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">LEADER OF THE PACK</h2>Varfa is accompanied by Orhu, her loyal companion. Companions are a new type of minion that have their own abilities. Level up Orhu to gain new abilities and assist you in combat.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1399020/extras/Untitled-6.png?t=1603351686\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">BE PREPARED</h2>Utilize a new type of tile, Traps, to setup and punish your foes. Arm traps on the board and then drop or push enemies into them to trigger their effect.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1399020/extras/traps2.png?t=1603351686\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">STEADY AIM</h2>Varfa is a master of dealing damage to enemies out of combat and she can utilize a new keyword, Mark, to target enemies. Marked enemies take additional damage from out of combat items and abilities, making them vulnerable to Varfa\u2019s ranged arsenal<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1399020/extras/mark.png?t=1603351686\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1399020/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1603351686","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1399020/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1603351686","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1399020/capsule_231x